\n476:   - Purpose: Verify delegation to dp_client.write_file\n477:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n478:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestWriteFile -v`\n479: \n480: - [ ] **T9.16**: Test upload_file delegation\n481:   - Purpose: Verify delegation to dp_client.upload_file\n482:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n483:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestUploadFile -v`\n484: \n485: - [ ] **T9.17**: Test download_file delegation\n486:   - Purpose: Verify delegation to dp_client.download_file\n487:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n488:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestDownloadFile -v`\n489: \n490: - [ ] **T9.18**: Test list_files delegation\n491:   - Purpose: Verify delegation to dp_client.list_files\n492:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n493:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestListFiles -v`\n494: \n495: - [ ] **T9.19**: Test stop closes data plane\n496:   - Purpose: Verify dp_client.close() called\n497:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n498:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestStop::test_stop_closes_data_plane -v`\n499: \n500: - [ ] **T9.20**: Test stop deletes control plane session\n501:   - Purpose: Verify cp_client.delete_session called when session_id set\n502:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n503:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestStop::test_stop_deletes_session -v`\n504: \n505: - [ ] **T9.21**: Test stop closes control plane\n506:   - Purpose: Verify cp_client.close() called\n507:   - File: `tests/test_code_interpreter.py`\n508:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestStop::test_stop_closes_control_plane -v`\n509: \n510: ### Phase 10: Integration Tests (ST-10)\n511: \n512: - [ ] **T10.1**: Test full session lifecycle with context manager\n513:   - Purpose: Verify create -> use -> cleanup flow\n514:   - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n515:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestSessionLifecycle -v`\n516: \n517: - [ ] **T10.2**: Test code execution workflow\n518:   - Purpose: Verify run_code returns output\n519:   - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n520:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestCodeExecution -v`\n521: \n522: - [ ] **T10.3**: Test file operations workflow\n523:   - Purpose: Verify write/upload/download/list files work together\n524:   - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n525:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestFileOperations -v`\n526: \n527: - [ ] **T10.4**: Test command execution with error handling\n528:   - Purpose: Verify CommandExecutionError raised on failure\n529:   - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n530:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestCommandError -v`\n531: \n532: - [ ] **T10.5**: Test session reuse across operations\n533:   - Purpose: Verify session_id reused across multiple operations\n534:   - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n535:   - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestSessionReuse -v`\n536: \n537: ---\n538: \n539: ## Task Dependencies\n540: \n541: ```\n542: Phase 1 (Exceptions) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n543: T1.1 (AgentCubeError) ──┬── T1.2 (CommandExecutionError)\n544:                         ├── T1.3 (SessionError)\n545:                         └── T1.4 (DataPlaneError)\n546: \n547: Phase 2 (Utilities) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n548: T2.1 (create_session) ──┬── T3.1 (ControlPlaneClient init)\n549:                         └── T4.1 (DataPlaneClient init)\n550: T2.2 (read_token) ──────┬── T3.2 (auth token resolution)\n551: T2.3 (get_logger) ──────┬── T5.1 (CodeInterpreterClient init)\n552: T2.4 (utils init) ──────┬── T6.1 (clients init)\n553: \n554: Phase 3 (ControlPlaneClient) ────────────────────────────────────────\n555: T3.1 (init) ──┬── T3.2 (auth token)\n556:               ├── T3.3 (Bearer header)\n557:               ├── T3.4 (URL resolution)\n558:               └── T3.5 (create_session)\n559:                          └── T3.6 (sessionId extraction)\n560:               ├── T3.7 (delete_session)\n561:                          └── T3.8 (404 handling)\n562:               └── T3.9 (close)\n563: \n564: Phase 4 (DataPlaneClient) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n565: T4.1 (init) ──┬── T4.2 (session header)\n566:               ├── T4.3 (base_url construction)\n567:               ├── T4.4 (execute_command)\n568:                          ├── T4.5 (timeout buffer)\n569:                          └── T4.6 (non-zero exit)\n570:               ├── T4.7 (write_file)\n571:               ├── T4.8 (upload_file)\n572:               ├── T4.9 (download_file)\n573:               ├── T4.10 (list_files)\n574:               └── T4.11 (close)\n575: \n576: Phase 5 (CodeInterpreterClient) ────────────────────────────────────────\n577: T5.1 (init) ──┬── T5.2 (Router URL required)\n578:               ├── T5.3 (router URL resolution)\n579:               ├── T5.4 (session reuse)\n580:               ├── T5.5 (session creation)\n581:               ├── T5.6 (data plane init)\n582:                          └── T5.7 (failure cleanup)\n583:               ├── T5.8 (__enter__)\n584:               ├── T5.9 (__exit__)\n585:               ├── T5.10-T5.16 (delegation methods)\n586:               └── T5.17 (stop)\n587: \n588: Phase 3-5 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n589: T3.1-T3.9 ────┬── T7.1-T7.12 (ControlPlane tests)\n590: T4.1-T4.11 ───┬── T8.1-T8.14 (DataPlane tests)\n591: T5.1-T5.17 ───┬── T9.1-T9.21 (CodeInterpreter tests)\n592: \n593: Phase 6 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n594: T1.1-T1.4 ────┬── T6.3 (exceptions exports)\n595: T3.1-T4.11 ───┬── T6.1 (clients exports)\n596: T5.1-T5.17 ───┬── T6.2 (top-level exports)\n597: \n598: Phase 7-9 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n599: T7.1-T7.12 ───┬── T10.1-T10.5 (integration)\n600: T8.1-T8.14 ───┬── T10.1-T10.5 (integration)\n601: T9.1-T9.21 ───┬── T10.1-T10.5 (integration)\n602: ```\n603: \n604: ---\n605: \n606: ## Verification Commands\n607: \n608: | Task | Verification Command |\n609: |------|----------------------|\n610: | Phase 1 | `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import *; print('OK')\"` |\n611: | Phase 2 | `pytest tests/test_utils.py -v` |\n612: | Phase 3 | `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py -v` |\n613: | Phase 4 | `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py -v` |\n614: | Phase 5 | `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py -v` |\n615: | Phase 6 | `python -c \"from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient; from agentcube.clients import *; print('OK')\"` |\n616: | Phase 7 | `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py -v` |\n617: | Phase 8 | `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py -v` |\n618: | Phase 9 | `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py -v` |\n619: | Phase 10 | `pytest tests/test_integration.py -v` |\n620: | All Tests | `pytest tests/ -v` |\n621: \n622: ---\n623: \n624: ## Acceptance Criteria\n625: \n626: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterClient.__init__` with `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `auth_token`, `verbose`, `session_id`\n627: - [ ] Router URL required: raises `ValueError` if missing via arg and env\n628: - [ ] Context manager: `__enter__` returns self, `__exit__` calls `stop()`\n629: - [ ] Session reuse: skips `create_session` when `session_id` provided\n630: - [ ] Data plane init failure cleanup: deletes session, logs warning, re-raises\n631: - [ ] `execute_command`: JSON body `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}`, read timeout buffer `+2.0`\n632: - [ ] Non-zero exit: raises `CommandExecutionError(exit_code, stderr, command)`\n633: - [ ] `run_code`: writes timestamped `.py` file, executes via `python3`\n634: - [ ] `write_file`: base64 content, mode `\"0644\"`\n635: - [ ] `upload_file`: multipart POST with `x-agentcube-session-id`\n636: - [ ] `download_file`: GET with `stream=True`\n637: - [ ] `list_files`: GET with query `path`\n638: - [ ] Session header: `x-agentcube-session-id` on all data plane requests\n639: - [ ] Control plane: `POST` `/v1/code-interpreter`, `DELETE` `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{id}`\n640: - [ ] `delete_session`: 404 returns `True`, other failures log and return `False`\n641: - [ ] Auth token: explicit arg or `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n642: - [ ] `Authorization: Bearer {token}` header when token present\n643: - [ ] Default timeouts: read `120s`, connect `5.0s`\n644: - [ ] Exception hierarchy: `AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError`, `SessionError`, `DataPlaneError`\n645: \n646: ---\n647: \n648: ## File Changes Summary\n649: \n650: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n651: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n652: | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Create | ~40 | Exception hierarchy classes |\n653: | `agentcube/utils/http.py` | Create | ~30 | HTTP session creation helper |\n654: | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | Create | ~20 | Token file reader helper |\n655: | `agentcube/utils/log.py` | Create | ~15 | Logger configuration helper |\n656: | `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Utils package exports |\n657: | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | Create | ~100 | ControlPlaneClient implementation |\n658: | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | Create | ~150 | CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient implementation |\n659: | `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Clients package exports |\n660: | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | Create | ~200 | CodeInterpreterClient implementation |\n661: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Modify | ~10 | Top-level package exports |\n662: | `tests/test_utils.py` | Create | ~50 | Utility module tests |\n663: | `tests/test_control_plane.py` | Create | ~150 | ControlPlaneClient unit tests |\n664: | `tests/test_data_plane.py` | Create | ~200 | DataPlaneClient unit tests |\n665: | `tests/test_code_interpreter.py` | Create | ~250 | CodeInterpreterClient unit tests |\n666: | `tests/test_integration.py` | Create | ~100 | Integration tests |\n667: \n668: ---\n669: \n670: ## Implementation Notes\n671: \n672: ### Session Header Convention\n673: \n674: All data plane requests use lowercase header name:\n675: ```python\n676: headers = {\"x-agentcube-session-id\": session_id}\n677: ```\n678: \n679: ### Timeout Buffer Strategy\n680: \n681: Execute command read timeout includes buffer to avoid `ReadTimeout` before PicoD returns exit 124:\n682: ```python\n683: read_timeout = timeout_value + 2.0  # 2 second buffer\n684: ```\n685: \n686: ### Base URL Construction\n687: \n688: Data plane base_url is constructed using `urljoin`:\n689: ```python\n690: base_url = urljoin(router_url, f\"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/\")\n691: ```\n692: \n693: ### Auth Token Resolution Order\n694: \n695: 1. Explicit `auth_token` argument\n696: 2. Kubernetes service account file: `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n697: \n698: ### Default Timeout Values\n699: \n700: | Timeout | Value | Purpose |\n701: |---------|-------|---------|\n702: | Read timeout | 120s | HTTP response read timeout |\n703: | Connect timeout | 5.0s | HTTP connection establishment |\n704: \n705: ### File Write Format\n706: \n707: ```python\n708: {\n709:     \"path\": \"/workspace/file.py\",\n710:     \"content\": base64.b64encode(content_bytes).decode(),\n711:     \"mode\": \"0644\"\n712: }\n713: ```\n714: \n715: ### Execute Command Format\n716: \n717: ```python\n718: {\n719:     \"command\": [\"python3\", \"/workspace/file.py\"],\n720:     \"timeout\": \"30s\"\n721: }\n722: ```\n723: \n724: ---\n725: \n726: ## Implementation Timeline\n727: \n728: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n729: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n730: | Phase 1: Exceptions | T1.1-T1.4 | Pending | 0% |\n731: | Phase 2: Utilities | T2.1-T2.4 | Pending | 0% |\n732: | Phase 3: ControlPlaneClient | T3.1-T3.9 | Pending | 0% |\n733: | Phase 4: DataPlaneClient | T4.1-T4.11 | Pending | 0% |\n734: | Phase 5: CodeInterpreterClient | T5.1-T5.17 | Pending | 0% |\n735: | Phase 6: Package Exports | T6.1-T6.3 | Pending | 0% |\n736: | Phase 7: ControlPlane Tests | T7.1-T7.12 | Pending | 0% |\n737: | Phase 8: DataPlane Tests | T8.1-T8.14 | Pending | 0% |\n738: | Phase 9: CodeInterpreter Tests | T9.1-T9.21 | Pending | 0% |\n739: | Phase 10: Integration | T10.1-T10.5 | Pending | 0% |\n740: \n741: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/80 tasks)**\n742: \n743: ---\n744: \n745: ## References\n746: \n747: - Design: `changes/AR-027/design.md`\n748: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md`\n749: - `python-sdk/design.md` — AgentCube Python SDK design\n750: - `python-sdk/spec.md` — AgentCube Python SDK specification\n\n(End of file - total 750 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient |\n| Module | `sdk-python` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed]\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Exception Hierarchy (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Implement `AgentCubeError` base exception class\n  - Purpose: Define base exception for all AgentCube SDK errors","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775880864229,"end":1775880864265}}}}
